---
title: Simple Stovetop Veggie 'Nduja Chorizo Mac & Cheese with Baby Leaf Salad and Cucumber
description: This Simple Stovetop Veggie 'Nduja Chorizo Mac & Cheese will be on your table in less than 25 minutes. Featuring a hot, umami blend of Calabrian chillies and peppers, this 'Nduja is completely meat-free but with all the same flavour.
